Here’s a **clean branch strategy** + exact command to create it.

---

## Branch Name (recommended)

```
feature/landing-readme-funnel
```

---

## Create + switch

```bash
git checkout -b feature/landing-readme-funnel
```

---

## What goes in this branch

**Files to add/update:**

```
/README.md                 → upgraded repo README
/docs/landing.md           → full landing page copy
/web/landing-page/         → (optional) actual frontend
```

---

## If pushing to remote

```bash
git push -u origin feature/landing-readme-funnel
```
